metadata.name: Listen - أصغي
metadata.description:
It all began when I started meditating.
It taught me to listen... to myself, to my body, to my soul.
The more I listen, the more I learn about listening. It comes in many forms. I'm learning that there's a lot more to learn.
I feel connected and present.
 I'm thankful and grateful that this connection has led me to this beautiful unfolding journey.
